</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-202_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">LXPs offer a wide range of interactive and engaging content, including videos, simulations, gamified modules, and social learning features. These elements not only make learning enjoyable but also increase retention and knowledge application.
