</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-206_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">LXPs deliver content in small, digestible chunks, following the principles of microlearning. This approach enables learners to consume information quickly and efficiently, fitting learning into their busy schedules.
